{"tid":312811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多人試過架𨋢層層都開門？","createTime":"2017-07-07T18:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T08:17:11.000Z","uid":47636,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc050d436bdb8a7fb6372f9e4a22a6da99c66bd","tid":312811,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:36:16.000Z","msg":"住嗰度一落大雨，潮濕，<br />\n<br />\n架𨋢就會神神地層層都停低開門。<br />\n<br />\n啱啱夜歸又嚟料，<br />\n<br />\n同個𡃁妹同一架𨋢，<br />\n<br />\n架𨋢17樓開始逐層停，<br />\n<br />\n要等佢開完門撳掣關翻再上，<br />\n<br />\n我到佢就知佢第一次遇到咁嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n見佢好似好緊張咁縮埋一角，<br />\n<br />\n驚開門有鬼還是有怪物衝入嚟咁嘅樣。<br />\n<br />\n如是者我到23樓出，見佢要上30樓，<br />\n<br />\n心諗幫你撳到呢度咋，陪你唔到啦𡃁妹。<br />\n<br />\n唔知佢一個人驚成點，真係陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿叔第一次咁嘅情況係某晚凌晨4點幾，<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣自己一丁友都有啲不安。<br />\n<br />\n但其實唔洗驚啦，試得多就慣咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過想問下，<br />\n<br />\n係得我住嗰度咁？定有冇人都試過？"},{"pid":"c548a71a87685cef935190fb1467fea163d67cd0","tid":312811,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:39:40.000Z","msg":"故黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25764c21108f6c027d98ccfd01cec795ce114aeb","tid":312811,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:41:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>故黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係啦，架𨋢好幾次落大雨都係咁，不論早晚"},{"pid":"181aaa7f9c838fedb84a88a5da6fdd18dc1d4c84","tid":312811,"uid":52474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:42:46.000Z","msg":"其實人地係驚你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749a4331a3fadea74ab0226ed958fa2d4f423c8b","tid":312811,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:43:15.000Z","msg":"勸你小心啲個女仔好啲...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7932e2c6fbcd442a55c9469d050009a5e8e297e","tid":312811,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:44:37.000Z","msg":"知唔知邊到有得整mon?"},{"pid":"22ad59111d6d5011a94cad78b32172b9748e154f","tid":312811,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T19:09:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實人地係驚你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係咁先23樓即走，我個樣真係好撚猥瑣下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84486c59c741a211b1d0e5a0918cb2970e040b3","tid":312811,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T19:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勸你小心啲個女仔好啲...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見過好多次㗎啦"},{"pid":"274b330585af979f0d4188eb1b2d57c53b48a2e7","tid":312811,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T19:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>知唔知邊到有得整mon?</blockquote><br />\n整𨋢下話？"},{"pid":"95fbc515a589a43debe0934e17bb03832ca6318d","tid":312811,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"你真係見到有人？"},{"pid":"08ad2739eed4a2c902c335498d1d80ca66f2f3ba","tid":312811,"uid":90415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T07:59:25.000Z","msg":"個𡃁妹見到一樣你見唔到嘅野"},{"pid":"e412b07d06e3981f1c644818c969d82dd6239a16","tid":312811,"uid":30249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:11:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個𡃁妹見到一樣你見唔到嘅野</blockquote><br />\n樓主自己個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3ad67f05bef2cefed3c23851babd4b2f47565f","tid":312811,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:17:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個𡃁妹見到一樣你見唔到嘅野</blockquote><br />\n樓主自己個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/a